OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776773466
OL,3,CDog owner handed animal ban after pets
OL,4,Csuffer 'hunting related injuries'
OL,6,FA man has been handed an animal ban
OL,7,Fafter he used his dogs to hunt foxes,
OL,8,Fhares, badgers, and deers.
OL,10,FJack Hindle handed himself in to
OL,11,FBlackburn Police station in December
OL,12,F2024 after officers attended his
OL,13,Faddress alongside the RSPCA.
OL,15,FThe 23-year-old from Burnley's crimes
OL,16,Fwere uncovered when footage was shared
OL,17,Fwith the RSPCA of his two lurchers
OL,18,FDoris and Woody fighting with local
OL,19,Fwildlife.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
