PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776773466
OL,3,CDog owner handed animal ban after pets
OL,4,Csuffer 'hunting related injuries'
OL,6,FWilliam Mitchell, RSPCA Special
OL,7,FOperations Unit Chief Inspector said:
OL,8,F"(The footage involved) dogs hunting
OL,9,Ffox, hare, badger and deer.
OL,11,F"There was evidence that (Doris and
OL,12,FWoody) had been used for hunting and I
OL,13,Fbelieved that those dogs had
OL,14,Frepeatedly been used for fighting with
OL,15,Fwildlife and received wounds as a
OL,16,Fresult of those fights."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@BpmpD@WpnsD@ZpmtD@FpnxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
