PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776773466
OL,3,CDog owner handed animal ban after pets
OL,4,Csuffer 'hunting related injuries'
OL,6,FAs a result of the videos, Hindle was
OL,7,Fcharged with four animal welfare
OL,8,Foffences, including two counts of
OL,9,Fwilfully killing or injuring a badger
OL,10,Fcontrary to the Protection of Badgers
OL,11,FAct 1992.
OL,13,FHindle was also charged with failing
OL,14,Fto take steps to protect his dog Doris
OL,15,Ffrom pain, suffering, and injury after
OL,16,Fa vet discovered she had been wounded,
OL,17,Flikely during a hunt.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
