OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776773466
OL,3,CDog owner handed animal ban after pets
OL,4,Csuffer 'hunting related injuries'
OL,6,FThe vet told a court that Doris had
OL,7,Fsuffered "a skin laceration to the
OL,8,Ffront of the left thigh area" and
OL,9,F"skin laceration with the skin torn
OL,10,Foutwards exposing the underlying
OL,11,Ftendons" on the right front paw.
OL,26,@pD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
