FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776773466
OL,3,CDog owner handed animal ban after pets
OL,4,Csuffer 'hunting related injuries'
OL,6,FThe vet also watched the videos of the
OL,7,Fdogs fighting wild animals, and told
OL,8,Fthe court: "The dogs engage with the
OL,9,Fwildlife, attacking and fighting
OL,10,Fwithout any attempt by their handlers
OL,11,Fto bring those dogs under close
OL,12,Fcontrol or prevent them from attacking
OL,13,Fthe wild animal. Such practice
OL,14,Frepeatedly exposes those dogs to
OL,15,Finjury."
OL,17,FRSPCA CI Mitchell also described a
OL,18,Fseries of video evidence, either sent
OL,19,Fto Hindle, or thought to have been
OL,20,Fcreated on his phone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
