PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776773466
OL,3,CDog owner handed animal ban after pets
OL,4,Csuffer 'hunting related injuries'
OL,6,FThese included videos showing
OL,7,F"injuries to Doris ... consistent with
OL,8,Fpossible hunting related injuries"
OL,9,Fwith further footage showing "Hindle
OL,10,Falluding to being involved with
OL,11,Fbaiting badgers".
OL,13,FDoris and Woody were taken into
OL,14,Fpossession of the police in December
OL,15,F2024.
OL,17,FIn mitigation, the length of time
OL,18,Fsince the offences took place was
OL,19,Freferred to, as well as the fact that
OL,20,FHindle has no previous offences.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@bO]qD@^OUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
