OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776773466
OL,3,CDog owner handed animal ban after pets
OL,4,Csuffer 'hunting related injuries'
OL,6,FHis youth was also referenced as a
OL,7,Fmitigating factor, as well as the fact
OL,8,Fthat he has autism.
OL,10,FAlongside the five-year ban, Hindle
OL,11,Fwas also handed a 12-month community
OL,12,Forder and must complete 15
OL,13,Frehabilitation days. The defendant was
OL,14,Falso ordered to pay #600 in costs, a
OL,15,Ffine of #80 and a #32 surcharge.
OL,17,FSpeaking after sentencing, CI Mitchell
OL,18,Fsaid: "The impact on both wildlife and
OL,19,Fdogs in this case is extremely
OL,20,Fupsetting.
OL,26,@zD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
