PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776773466
OL,3,CDog owner handed animal ban after pets
OL,4,Csuffer 'hunting related injuries'
OL,6,F"All animals deserve to be treated
OL,7,Fwith kindness and compassion and this
OL,8,Fresult should act as a warning that
OL,9,Fsuch behaviour will not be tolerated."
